Feature/Improvement - Anything not currently in the product, but should be.
Copy/Content - Indicates some content needs to be created or acquired (i.e., writing up FAQs, getting employee info)
Product - Anything related to product management (i.e., deciding pricing models)

Bug/Tech Debt/Blocked - Bug is something that is broken and needs fixing. Tech Debt is any feature that operates in a way that is less than ideal, though may not necessarily be broken. Blocked is anything that is blocking the development of future work.
Design - Anything related to UI, UX, illustration, etc.
Development - Covers all elements of development from ops, front-end development, DB architecture, etc.
